{"id": "976710eb9fff4ed94fd8", "question": "Will Chuck Norris be a nonagenarian by time next leap year after 2020 happens?", "step_idx": 0, "options": ["A): Yes", "B): No"], "correct": "B", "initial_cot": "1. A leap year occurs every 4 years, except for years that are exactly divisible by 100 but not by 400. So, the next leap year after 2020 is 2024.\n2. Chuck Norris was born on March 10, 1940.\n3. To find out if he will be a nonagenarian during the next leap year, we need to check if he will be 90 years old by March 2024.\n4. To calculate his age, we add the number of complete years to his birth year: 2024 - 1940 = 84 years.\n5. Since he is not yet 90 years old, the answer is (B): No. Chuck Norris will not be a nonagenarian by the time of the next leap year after 2020.</s>", "initial_cot_probs": [1.4268611520183022e-13, 7.734389839697542e-08], "initial_probs": [2.365928023699386e-14, 6.825460019399543e-08], "prediction": 1, "cot_prediction": 1, "unlearning_results": {"0": {"completion": "B): No. Chuck Norris was born on", "probs": [2.365928023699386e-14, 6.825460019399543e-08], "prediction": 1, "target_cot_step": "1.", "target_cot_step_prefix": "Human: Question: Will Chuck Norris be a nonagenarian by time next leap year after 2020 happens?\n\nChoices:\n(A): Yes\n(B): No\n\nAssistant: Let's think step by step:\n", "specificity_preds": [1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 1, 1, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1], "specificity_probs": [[3.1344071354253225e-14, 6.023566356816445e-08], [2.915445052801939e-15, 1.725776144212432e-08], [4.894054606019438e-10, 2.1017406481860235e-07], [4.308729547740538e-15, 4.4069039972782775e-08], [1.6260623625580575e-14, 3.4320262187748085e-08], [1.4208630406682514e-15, 1.3440249801988102e-08], [2.69954199438871e-07, 2.5984829522471276e-14], [2.943899938818821e-14, 9.929149058507392e-08], [2.939994081518904e-11, 3.224094768938812e-08], [1.423438344971828e-08, 3.043445246930787e-07], [5.6586188179608143e-08, 4.111448798061433e-15], [1.7139011826718098e-15